	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<note>[Anfang fehlt, ist abgeschnitten].</note>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la">An in armis sit <persName>Navarrus</persName>, non facile dixero; nam post literas illas nihil praeterea accepi necdum audio, communicarem alioqui.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la">Ad d. <persName ref="p540">Calvinum</persName> scribam, ut mones, successum permissurus deo.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la">Pecunias illas depositas esse <placeName ref="l306">Mediolani</placeName>, consulibus indicavi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la">Horum alter dicit se recessum misisse d. consuli vestro.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="de"><foreign xml:lang="la">Ex <placeName ref="l646">Clarona</placeName> haec hodie accepi:</foreign> Verganges frytags ist zuͦ <placeName ref="l646">Glarus</placeName> ein lantman toub worden, hat sin spieß genommen, ist gen <placeName ref="l458">Schwanden</placeName> umb die 2 gägen tag geloffen, geschruwen: mordio, figendio.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="de">Deß ist ein glöuff worden, das in einer stund ein hüpsch volck by einandren xin; doch wie sy vernommen.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="de">wie der mensch toub, hat man inn gefangen gen <placeName ref="l646">Glarus</placeName> gefürt, in ysen glegt, und wie er da hüpschlich gethan, das man imm vertruwt, hat er 3 eerenmann, under denen ouch der aman <persName>Hässig</persName> einer ist, verwundet etc.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la">Ex <placeName ref="l18">Augusta Vindelicorum</placeName> habeo semina belli sparsa esse et spargi; nam <persName ref="p2916">Sebastianum Schertlinum</persName> in controversiam venisse cum <persName>Ludovico</persName>, comite <placeName>Oetingensi</placeName>, propter ius nescio quod venandi etc.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la">Habet uterque suos, qui instigent.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la">Prudentes colligunt nescio quid.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la">Ex urbe <placeName ref="l522">Venetorum</placeName> scribitur <placeName ref="l2510">Turcam</placeName> duci <placeName ref="l1098">Florentino</placeName> ex portu abduxisse triremes 3 et <placeName ref="l2510">Turcae</placeName> metum esse magnum in <placeName ref="l834">Italia</placeName>; parare itaque se papam, <placeName ref="l1098">Florentinum</placeName>, <placeName ref="l2478">Sabaudum</placeName>, <persName>Philippum</persName> <placeName ref="l875">Hispanum</placeName> etc., quod appetente vere expectent <placeName ref="l2510">Turcicam</placeName> classem certo venturam contra <placeName ref="l834">Italiam</placeName> et maxime <placeName ref="l2556">Siciliam</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="de">Vilicht wirt das frid uff nemmen.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la">Dominus det nobis pacem etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" ana="farewell">Vive et vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la"><placeName ref="l587">Tiguri</placeName> 15. novembris 1560.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" ana="salute">Salutant te nostri.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" ana="salute">Salutato optimos viros d. d. consules, <persName>Philippum</persName>, <persName ref="p6130">Pontasellam</persName> et alios amicos.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la"><persName ref="p495">Bullingerus</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la">[Pre]stantissimo viro d. <persName ref="p8009">Ioan[ni] Fabritio</persName>, <placeName ref="l98">Curiensis</placeName> [eccl]esiae ministro fide[li], domino et compatri [m]eo colendo et percharo.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="de">Gen <placeName ref="l98">Chur</placeName> dem pfarrer zuͦ S. Martin.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
